<p>Whether we&rsquo;re reporting on the impacts of the COVID-19 crisis or lifting up the movements fighting against climate destruction, corporate profiteering and authoritarianism, it&rsquo;s critical that we get the facts out. But we can&rsquo;t do it without the support of our readers.</p>
