<h2 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">
<a href="https://truthout.org/articles/here-are-seven-brilliant-insights-from-noam-chomsky-on-american-empire/">Here Are Seven Brilliant Insights From Noam Chomsky on the American Empire</a>
</h2>
</div>
<div class="entry-summary" itemprop="description">
<div>
<div class="entry-summary">As Trump strikes Syria for the second time, here are seven powerful quotes from Dr. Chomsky.</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="entry-meta">
<dl class="article__authors byline">
