<a class="archive-image" href="https://truthout.org/articles/noam-chomsky-on-the-populist-groundswell-us-elections-the-future-of-humanity-and-more/" title="Noam Chomsky on the Populist Groundswell, US Elections and the Future of Humanity">
<img width="400" height="300" src="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Noam-Chomsky-on-the-Populist-Groundswell-US-Elections-and-the-Future-of-Humanity-400x300.jpg" class="attachment-sd_medium size-sd_medium" alt="" loading="lazy" srcset="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Noam-Chomsky-on-the-Populist-Groundswell-US-Elections-and-the-Future-of-Humanity-400x300.jpg 400w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Noam-Chomsky-on-the-Populist-Groundswell-US-Elections-and-the-Future-of-Humanity-200x150.jpg 200w" sizes="(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px" />
