<div class="before-headline">
<div class='categories'>
<a href='https://truthout.org/category/interview/' rel='category' class='interview'>Interview</a>
</div>
<div class='sections'>
<a href='https://truthout.org/section/politics-and-elections/' rel='section' class='politics-and-elections' style='color: #1958aa;'>Politics &amp; Elections</a>
</div>
</div>
<div class="">
<h2 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">
<a href="https://truthout.org/articles/noam-chomsky-on-the-populist-groundswell-us-elections-the-future-of-humanity-and-more/">Noam Chomsky on the Populist Groundswell, US Elections and the Future of Humanity</a>
</h2>
</div>
<div class="entry-summary" itemprop="description">
<div>
<div class="entry-summary">Noam Chomsky on where we stand as an economy, as a country and as human beings.</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="entry-meta">
<dl class="article__authors byline">
<dt class="meta-label">by </dt>
